Package com.atakmap.android.cotdelete

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CotDeleteEventMarshal
    TAK capability to process the t-x-d-d CoT event to delete a map item within the system.
    CotDeleteImporter
    Supports making markers stale based on a CoT Delete task <__forcedelete/> The key parts of this message are the type (t-x-d-d) the link attribute populated and the optional __forcedelete tag.
